---
title: Super Speedy Turkey Udon with teriyaki sauce and sugar snaps
description: This tangy teriyaki turkey mince dish has plenty of crunch thanks to sugar snaps and bell pepper. There's also plenty of flavour, which is a good thing, as, the udon noodles that accompany happen to be great for soaking up strong sauces such as the umami teriyaki in this recipe.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R25_W29_IE_IEQT24272-3_Main_high-abd5d751.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ie/recipecards/card/6630dc467e315d77eb46da1e-en-IE.pdf
servings: 2
